"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"its highest level\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The crowds set to descend on Paris will be in marked contrast to the atmosphere of the last Summer Olympics in Tokyo in 2021 which played to empty arenas, and a year later than scheduled, due to the COVID-19 pandemic.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.093294937215571e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2261, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999963038135, \"rank\": 2.9556440497518446e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999974244075446, \"rank\": 2.513784389514199e-06, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The crowds\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"marked contrast\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"the last Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"empty arenas\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French officials have said there are no specific terrorism threats for the ceremony that will launch the Games in Paris, which run until Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2369, \"end